{"tid":1604466,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鼠王芬暗示香港無\"高度自治\"?","createTime":"2019-09-30T03:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T03:33:09.000Z","uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c60d814ca06623882eb7cd22d60f2329f9dbe0a6","tid":1604466,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:27:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483345-20190930.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483345-20190930.htm&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1XbrkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=090a004f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483345-20190930.htm&h=38157abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483345-20190930.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n國慶觀禮團分批前往北京，觀禮團成員之一的經民聯立法會議員梁美芬在機場被問到，會否向中央提出給予特區政府更多空間進行政改。梁美芬說，今次風波源於反修例，暴力示威者不應加入其他訴求，脅迫政府，又說現時暴力掩蓋討論空間。<br />\n<br />\n對於在國慶前後數天有網民發起示威活動，她呼籲不要用暴力，如果想爭取高度自治或重啟政改，首先要與暴力切割，否則相關討論不能展開。<br />\n<br />\n至於上周舉行的首場政府社區對話會，梁美芬說，社區對話不是一次就見成效，雙方都要有橄欖枝，如果暴力升級，很難尋求中間方案，會破壞協調和對話的氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，肯定第一場公開對話，認為政府和市民之間的信任低，要舉行多場及不同形式對話，例如匿名或網上對話，雙方都要有誠意，否則對話有難度。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬認為政治是妥協藝術，如果社會希望制度朝向開放發展，暴力是一條絕路，只會令想改善制度的人卻步，所以要與暴力切割。"},{"pid":"39a4c8d4331ce6bdf27fe3254e11aa0e0bace63d","tid":1604466,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eYXN7uT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeYXN7uT.jpg&h=8ce194f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CA0H3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CA0H3e.jpg&h=879be3a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXwGsuV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXwGsuV.jpg&h=eaf524a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0185cc22ed3bdfc7027c0fa819f47779913387a","tid":1604466,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/urnyjrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Furnyjrp.jpg&h=11169d25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2421747b94fc37915ccdce90abf1d9a19c3d77b","tid":1604466,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:33:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}